{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/arch-linux-installation/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Hi, aphage"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"d1b328e9-015e-5f1b-9a32-616216fdcf9b","excerpt":"官方安装教程 参考1 参考2 分区 键盘布局 控制台键盘布局默认为 us（美式键盘映射）。列出所有可用的键盘布局，可以使用： 如果您想要更改键盘布局，可以将一致的文件名添加进 loadkeys(1)，但请省略路径和扩展名。比如，要添加 German 键盘布局：","html":"<p><a href=\"https://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php/Installation_guide_(%E7%AE%80%E4%BD%93%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87)\">官方安装教程</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://blog.yoitsu.moe/arch-linux/installing_arch_linux_for_complete_newbies.html\">参考1</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://shenyu.me/2020/04/11/arch-uefi-install.html\">参考2</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php/Partitioning_(%E7%AE%80%E4%BD%93%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87)#%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9_GPT_%E8%BF%98%E6%98%AF_MBR\">分区</a></p>\n<h2>键盘布局</h2>\n<p>控制台键盘布局默认为 us（美式键盘映射）。列出所有可用的键盘布局，可以使用：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">ls</span> /usr/share/kbd/keymaps/**/*.map.gz</code></pre></div>\n<p>如果您想要更改键盘布局，可以将一致的文件名添加进 loadkeys(1)，但请省略路径和扩展名。比如，要添加 German 键盘布局：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">loadkeys de-latin1</code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"Arch Linux Installation","date":"December 07, 2020","description":null}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/use-vcpkg/use-vcpkg/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"使用Vcpkg进行包管理"}},"next":null},"pageContext":{"id":"d1b328e9-015e-5f1b-9a32-616216fdcf9b","previousPostId":"665c4d09-3b24-5b90-8270-c366d5ccab0c","nextPostId":null}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383","916993862"]}